	(68,'Hitting it out of the park: family businesses can win by thinking like a baseball team','','June 9, 2014','David Fabian, Special to Financial Post \r\nMore from Special to Financial Post','<p>\n	Baseball season is in full swing, and fans across the country are enjoying another summer of cheering for their favourite teams. But, as any baseball fan knows, the chance of their team making the World Series is slim without the right mix of players, training and support. In the same way, family business owners need to identify and hone in on those key elements in their business strategy to win the close games.</p>\n<p>\n	In baseball, a team doesn&rsquo;t become a World Series contender by chance. Similarly, growth in business &ndash; especially in the current economy &ndash; is challenging. Establishing a loyal customer base, combined with a commitment to continuous innovation, can help family businesses distinguish themselves from their competitors and stand out across industries.</p>\n<p>\n	For most businesses, there typically comes a time when a decision needs to be made about whether to maintain current growth levels or to expand. While growth isn&rsquo;t always the safest or simplest option, it is essential to achieve market penetration and long term competitiveness. In baseball, we&rsquo;ve seen teams disappear because they didn&rsquo;t grow. But in baseball and in business, by evaluating &ndash; and re-evaluating &ndash; the business plan before taking the leap to grow, the risks associated with getting to the next level can be drastically reduced.</p>\n','0','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',0),
	(70,'Apple poaches Tag Heuer executive and more: All we know about the iWatch so far','http://tech.firstpost.com/news-analysis/apple-poaches-tag-heuer-executive-and-more-all-we-know-about','Jul-07- 2014 ','By Naina Khedekar ','<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; line-height: 32px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">\n	In the last couple of months, rumours around the alleged Apple iWatch have begun to accelerate. The latest one talks about Apple hiring luxury&nbsp;<strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><a href=\"http://tech.firstpost.com/news-analysis/apple-hires-tag-heuer-executive-with-the-iwatch-expected-to-launch-in-october-226933.html\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(238, 84, 63); background: transparent;\" target=\"_blank\">watch-maker Tag Heuer</a></strong>, for its rumoured stylish smartwatch. It is highly speculated that the iWatch won&rsquo;t be only about health and fitness, but also about good looks, aesthetics and luxury.</p>\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; line-height: 32px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; line-height: 32px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">\n	The watch is known to be capable of tracking heath-related factors, and also speculated to serve as a complete hub.&nbsp;Besides, it is also expected&nbsp;to perform some functions independently, but tasks like messaging and voice chat will require some connection to a smartphone. While Apple has been tight-lipped about its rumoured fitness-focused watch, a lot is being said and written about the wearable.&nbsp;<span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5em; background: transparent;\">From multiple iWatch designs to its release date, there have been speculations about it all. In fact,&nbsp;a comprehensive profile of Apple chief Tim Cook, earlier last month, talked about everything from his childhood memories to his work on human rights, alongside some hitherto unknown&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://tech.firstpost.com/news-analysis/apples-iwatch-is-real-and-its-reportedly-coming-in-q4-225870.html\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(238, 84, 63); line-height: 1.5em; background: transparent;\" target=\"_blank\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">details about the rumoured iWatch</strong></a><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5em; background: transparent;\">.</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; line-height: 32px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://klass.com/uploads/ckeditor_images/1404714133_iwatchconcept-624x350.jpeg\" style=\"width: 178px; height: 100px; float: left;\" /></p>\n<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; line-height: 32px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">\n	<span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5em; background: transparent;\">Here&rsquo;s a quick rumour-roundup for all we know about the iWatch, so far.</span></p>\n','0','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',0),
